ags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Galadriel\u2019s kickass orc-fighting has unexpected weight, considering the orc babies at home", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-09-06T04:01:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Astro Bot flies toward one of the hidden levels in the Tentacle System\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Team Asobi/PlayStation Studios via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/09/astro-bot-hidden-levels.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">There are multiple <strong>hidden levels</strong> in <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/astro-bot/445530\">Astro Bot</a></em>, which primarily take the form as hidden planets in each nebula. You\u2019ll need to unveil them if you want to complete every level and rescue every <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/447162\">bot</a>. The trick is, you might not even know you\u2019re missing a planet until you complete the nebula and see you\u2019ve somehow missed a few bots and puzzle pieces on the progress screen.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">In this", "id": 1092679, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/astro-bot-guides/447107/hidden-levels-planets-all-locations-how-to-unlock", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 258, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "All hidden levels in Astro Bot and how to unlock them", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-09-06T04:01:00+00:00", "desc